para_trans: Land Acquisition, Rehabilitation and Resettlement Authority, Nagpur
A total of 13 temporary posts in this office are as on date.
Citation No. - RPA-2024 / Q. No.56 / R-1
Martyr Rajguru Chowk, Madam Cama Road,
Read: - Government Decision, Revenue & Forest Department No. RPA-2024 / P.No.56 / R-1, D. 04.04.2024
Read above the table in the statement attached to the government decision here for land acquisition, resettlement and rehabilitation.
A total of 13 posts in various cadres sanctioned for the Rehabilitation Authority, Nagpur have been extended.
The details of these posts are given in the prospectus. Read this in the Government Decision Statement here.
"Driver and Sepoy" instead of "Driver (by source) and Sepoy (by source)" at 6. & 7.
Also, the government decision number should read "RPA-2019" instead of "RPA-2024."
